snippet.description:
Download: https://gamebanana.com/mods/560625

Mod Credits:
Tilesets By: Nintendo, Rimea, B1 Gaming, CodeMorio, NewerTeam
Music By: Nintendo, Square Enix, Lego City Undercover Team, Binding Of Isaac Team
NSMBWer+ By: RyGuy, King Pixel, Newer Team
Playtesters: Electrical Squid, Deku Knut, Qualiqola

Creators Featured In Trailer:
@MayroSMM https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WxuUs2lNy60&t=1s
@Deku_Knuthttps://www.twitch.tv/deku_knut
@ElectricalSquid https://youtu.be/Le62ixHf42A?si=anMDvomC7z72vbMT
@NinTyler https://youtu.be/PjLnWWTzzTY?si=UaQw6CVSp53PNU1R
@GCNathann https://youtu.be/PXvIkRjGY6U?si=SX6DCx6-uNRT1IWW 

4 Years of Making this mod, after various different versions and it even being a different name at one point. I'm still amazed over 4 years later, I'm still working on this project. 

NSMBW Superstar Mode is a mod made by Dread Modders, Who consists of Violet (Previously Jaiden_Spl) and 5 Points. We're just two friends having fun modding a game we truly love. This mod was started by Violet back in 2020, and has evolved a lot since its first release back in 2020 as Chaos Edition. But regardless, i'm happy with the state of the mod right now, and I can't wait to show off more. Maybe it also won't be such a long wait until the next Trailer. But we'll see. 

Mod Creators:
@VioletNATP 
@ChagasFivePoints 

This mod is not affiliated with Nintendo in any way. We do not own NSMBW, or Mario and Characters affiliated with Nintendo. Please support Nintendo for the amazing games they make!

No WBFS or ISO Will be provided or either the mod or Base game. Anyone who makes a WBFS or ISO version of the mod and publicly releases it is NOT from us.

